Class AuburnReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.impinj.octanesdk.ImpinjReader
      • AuburnReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.impinj.octanesdk.KeepaliveTimeoutListener, org.llrp.ltk.net.LLRPEndpoint

    public class AuburnReader
extends com.impinj.octanesdk.ImpinjReader
    AuburnReader is a child of the ImpinjReader documented in Impinj's OctaneSDK for Java. This class adds functionality to an RFID reader that allows the retrieval of the reader's location.
    Since:
    2-3-2015
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Sean Spurlin
